## WHAT iS Dom implementation ?
The DOM (Document Object Model) implementation in JavaScript is a programming interface (API) that allows scripts to dynamically access and update the content, structure, and style of a web document.
# 🎨 Color Greeting App

## 📌 Project Description

This is a simple interactive web page built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (DOM)** as part of my Tutedude Assignment.

The main idea of this project is to understand how JavaScript interacts with HTML elements using the DOM.

---

## 🚀 Features

* User can enter their name and get a personalized greeting
* Four interactive boxes (Red, Blue, Green, Yellow)
* Clicking on a box fills it with its respective color
* Clean and modern UI with hover effects

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML
* CSS (Flexbox, transitions, gradients)
* JavaScript (DOM manipulation, event handling)

---

## 📚 What I Learned

* How to select elements using DOM (`getElementById`, `querySelectorAll`)
* Handling user input
* Using `addEventListener` for click events
* Changing content dynamically using JavaScript
* Applying styles dynamically using JS

---

## ▶️ How to Run the Project

1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open the project folder in VS Code
3. Run the `index.html` file in your browser

---

## 💡 Future Improvements

* Add reset button
* Add animations on click
* Store user name using localStorage
* Improve UI with more advanced design

